Place Brother QL driver .deb packages here before building the cups Docker image.

Download from https://support.brother.com for your printer model (e.g. QL-800):
  - brother-QL800lpr-<version>.i386.deb   (LPR driver)
  - cupswrapperQL800-<version>.i386.deb   (CUPS wrapper)

These are i386 packages that work on amd64 hosts (via multiarch support).
For arm64 hosts, download the corresponding ARM packages instead.

Files in this directory are NOT committed to git (see .gitignore).
